---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';

// === Turnstile Audio, faithful rebuild of monuments.cc/portfolio/turnstile ===
// Real assets pulled from the live site into /public/case-studies/turnstile/{bts,products,brand}.
const bts = Array.from({ length: 10 }, (_, i) => `/case-studies/turnstile/bts/bts-${String(i + 1).padStart(2, '0')}.jpg`);
const products = Array.from({ length: 8 }, (_, i) => `/case-studies/turnstile/products/prod-${String(i + 1).padStart(2, '0')}.jpg`);
const services = ['Brand Identity', 'Logo Design', 'Brand Positioning', 'Consulting'];
const tags = ['Brand Development'];
---
<Base title="Turnstile Audio · monuments">
  <article class="cs2">

    <!-- HERO -->
    <header class="cs2-hero">
      <div class="cs2-hero-bg" style={`background-image:url(${bts[1]})`}></div>
      <div class="cs2-hero-scrim"></div>
      <div class="cs2-hero-inner">
        <h1 class="cs2-hero-title">Turnstile<br>Audio</h1>
        <div class="cs2-hero-foot">
          <div class="cs2-tags">{tags.map((t) => <span class="cs2-tag">{t}</span>)}</div>
          <a class="cs2-allwork" href="/work">All Work <span aria-hidden="true">↗</span></a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <img class="cs2-hero-mark" src="/case-studies/turnstile/brand/logo-mark.png" alt="Turnstile mark" />
    </header>

    <!-- INTRO: services sidebar + lead -->
    <section class="cs2-intro fade">
      <aside class="cs2-side">
        <h2 class="cs2-side-h">Turnstile Audio, Crafting a brand that hits all the right notes.</h2>
        <ul class="cs2-services">{services.map((s) => <li>{s}</li>)}</ul>
      </aside>
      <div class="cs2-intro-body">
        <p>When Turnstile Audio came to me, they wanted a brand identity that struck the perfect balance: clean, simple, and inspired by the legendary audio brands of the past, but fresh enough to stand out in today's market. They didn't want flashy, they wanted timeless. Something that communicated quality and craftsmanship without overcomplicating things, and felt welcoming to both up-and-coming creators and seasoned pros alike.</p>
        <p class="cs2-intro-kick">Our timeline? Two weeks to design, iterate, and launch.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- LOGO CARD + lockups -->
    <section class="cs2-logo fade">
      <div class="cs2-logo-card">
        <img src="/case-studies/turnstile/brand/wordmark.png" alt="Turnstile Audio" />
      </div>
      <div class="cs2-logo-aside">
        <img class="cs2-wordmark" src="/case-studies/turnstile/brand/wordmark.png" alt="Turnstile Audio wordmark" />
        <p class="cs2-logo-note">A single mark, three weights, confident, geometric, built to last just like the gear.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- BTS PHOTO GRID -->
    <section class="cs2-gallery">
      <div class="cs2-gallery-badge" aria-hidden="true">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 100 100"><defs><path id="tsBadge" d="M50,50 m-34,0 a34,34 0 1,1 68,0 a34,34 0 1,1 -68,0" /></defs>
          <text><textPath href="#tsBadge" startOffset="0%">IN ACTION · BEHIND THE BUILD · </textPath></text>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <div class="cs2-grid">
        {bts.map((src, i) => <figure class={`cs2-cell c-${i % 6}`}><img src={src} alt="" loading="lazy" /></figure>)}
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CONCEPT / DESIGN / DELIVER -->
    <section class="cs2-cdd fade">
      <h2 class="cs2-cdd-head"><span class="on">Concept</span> <span>Design</span> <span>Deliver</span></h2>
      <div class="cs2-cdd-cols">
        <div class="cs2-cdd-col">
          <p>When Turnstile Audio came to me, they wanted a brand identity that struck the perfect balance: clean, simple, and inspired by the legendary audio brands of the past, but fresh enough to stand out in today's market. They didn't want flashy, they wanted timeless.</p>
          <p>We took a deep dive into the world of vintage audio brands (what made them iconic and enduring) then built something confident, modern, and a little nostalgic, without trying too hard.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="cs2-cdd-col">
          <p class="cs2-obj-h">Objectives</p>
          <ul class="cs2-obj">
            <li>Craft a brand identity that captures Turnstile's ethos of precision, quality, and affordability.</li>
            <li>Design something that feels understated but undeniably cool, a nod to the classics.</li>
            <li>Let the gear be the star; the brand quietly amplifies the message under a two-week timeline.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CREDITS -->
    <div class="cs2-credits fade">
      <div><span>Agency</span>Art of Visuals</div>
      <div><span>Client</span>Adorama</div>
      <div><span>Creative Direction</span>DJ Ramirez</div>
    </div>

    <!-- PRODUCT GRID -->
    <section class="cs2-products">
      <span class="cs2-check" aria-hidden="true">CHECK CHECK</span>
      <div class="cs2-prod-grid">
        {products.map((src) => <figure class="cs2-prod"><img src={src} alt="" loading="lazy" /></figure>)}
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- NEXT PROJECT -->
    <a class="cs2-next" href="/work/blue-cross">
      <div class="cs2-next-bg" style={`background-image:url(${bts[8]})`}></div>
      <div class="cs2-next-scrim"></div>
      <div class="cs2-next-inner">
        <span class="cs2-next-k">Next project</span>
        <span class="cs2-next-t">Blue Cross of Idaho <span aria-hidden="true">→</span></span>
      </div>
    </a>

    <!-- CTA -->
    <section class="cs2-cta">
      <p>Let's build something great together.</p>
      <a href="/contact" class="cs2-cta-link">Let's Talk <span aria-hidden="true">↗</span></a>
    </section>

  </article>
</Base>
